data.description:
5 BEDROOM 3.5 BATH NEW CONSTRUCTION HOME IN NEW NEIGHBORHOOD. LARGE OPEN KITCHEN WITH GRANITE COUNTERS AND STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES. FEATURES HUGE MASTER BEDROOM AND MASTER BATH WITH SETTING AREA. BEST RENTAL IN FULTON COUNTY.

Rent does not include HOA fees, which are $600/year. This property allows self guided viewing without an appointment. Contact for details.
